OL,3,CCultural food bank struggling to meet
OL,4,Cdemand as Eid approaches
OL,6,FOne of the only cultural food banks in
OL,7,FWales has said it is struggling to
OL,8,Fmeet demand.
OL,10,FFeed Newport specialises in food
OL,11,Fparcels for people who have specific
OL,12,Fcultural needs, such as providing
OL,13,Fhalal food.
OL,15,FAs Eid approaches next week, the food
OL,16,Fbank is appealing for donations.
