OL,3,CCultural food bank struggling to meet
OL,4,Cdemand as Eid approaches
OL,6,F"We're having unfortunately to decline
OL,7,Ffood parcel referrals coming in from
OL,8,Fsupport workers, and people that are
OL,9,Fjust generally in need, whether
OL,10,Fthey're from the Muslim community,
OL,11,FChristian community, anywhere across
OL,12,FNewport," Gemma Walker, manager of
OL,13,FFeed Newport said.
OL,15,FShe added that the food bank put out
OL,16,Fan appeal for donations a few weeks
OL,17,Fago as there has been a decline in the
OL,18,Fnumber of donations.
