OL,3,CCultural food bank struggling to meet
OL,4,Cdemand as Eid approaches
OL,6,F"Our food bank isn't government
OL,7,Ffunded, it actually relies on the
OL,8,Fpublic donations that we have coming
OL,9,Fin. Obviously, everyone is struggling
OL,10,Fright now, so our food bank is
OL,11,Fstruggling," Gemma added.
OL,13,FThe food bank started up in February
OL,14,F2020 and continued throughout the
OL,15,FCoronavirus pandemic.
OL,17,FBased in Newport, the hub has also
OL,18,Fstarted a coffee shop and a skills
OL,19,Facademy, where people can learn
OL,20,Fbarista skills.
