OL,3,CCultural food bank struggling to meet
OL,4,Cdemand as Eid approaches
OL,6,FA soup kitchen is offered every
OL,7,FFriday, and the hub says they provide
OL,8,Faround 30 halal cooked breakfasts
OL,9,Fwithin two hours each Friday.
OL,11,F"Recently, I've had a shift in my job
OL,12,Fwhich has reduced my hours. It means
OL,13,Fmy finances and all my disposable
OL,14,Fincome aren't really there any more,"
OL,15,FShadir Hussein, who uses the food
OL,16,Fbank, said.
OL,18,F"Paying the bills is a big struggle
OL,19,Fnow, so juggling finances and trying
OL,20,Fto make ends meet is not really the
OL,21,Fsame any more.
