OL,3,CCultural food bank struggling to meet
OL,4,Cdemand as Eid approaches
OL,6,F"I noticed they (the food bank) were
OL,7,Foffering an Eid parcel because we've
OL,8,Fgot Eid coming up soon, so I felt that
OL,9,Fwould hopefully help me and my family."
OL,11,FFor Feed Newport, the number of people
OL,12,Fusing the food bank currently
OL,13,Foutweighs the supplies.
OL,15,F"Unfortunately, we're not getting the
OL,16,Fdonations in, the funding is hard to
OL,17,Fcome by these days. It breaks my
OL,18,Fheart," Gemma said.
